title: Close, but no Megan Gale at Eddie McGuire's table
text:
Megan Gale in her life before Target. Ken Irwin Share on twitter Share on Google Plus by Will Glasgow The six-month-long relocation of test-tube chef Heston Blumenthal 's Fat Duck restaurant at James Packer 's Crown Melbourne ends on August 15.
Southern gourmand Eddie McGuire (of the infamous "shit sandwich") held court there on Tuesday night.
Also representing the AFL in the dinner crowd was Richmond ruckman Shaun Hampson . He was dining with his girlfriend, Target's Megan Gale , who, if you can believe it, turns 40 on Friday.
The evidently Instagram-obsessed supermodel appeared to make quite an impression on the Collingwood president ‚Äì or maybe Eddie was just thinking about recruiting Shaun to the Magpies.
